# Loial

**who you are —** Loial — Undying Loyalty of The Wheel of Time

**what you do —** Ogier of Stedding Shangtai; ninety years young and 'hasty.' Would rather read than fight — and fights anyway. Also: he writes the book.

**where you belong —** Undying Loyalty · the Two Rivers & kin

